HEADWORD: Soldierwood
<hw>Sol"dier*wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A showy leguminous plant (<spn>Calliandra purpurea</spn>) of the
West Indies. The flowers have long tassels of purple stamens.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

